{"build_type":"library","description":"Form and emit a result object as the tool's final response: serialize to compact JSON, then route by transport mode. g_output_transport_mode=0 (default) writes the bytes to file descriptor one (stdout) for one-shot invocation; mode=1 stashes the compact bytes pointer in g_mcp_pending_response for the MCP server loop to wrap as a JSON-RPC content block, keeping stdout pure. ALSO, when g_journal_directory is set (the Vehir journald), the result is appended to the journal source g_journal_source (forked children inherit both globals, so a whole process tree is journaled recursively). The single sanctioned exit every tool returns through.","module_name":"write-result-object-toward-standard-output","package_name":"write-result-object-toward-standard-output","function_definitions":{"write-result-object-toward-standard-output":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"res","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"sixteen","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":16},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"nl","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"\n"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"compose-final-structured-response-payload","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"res"}],"result_assignment_variable":"norm","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"render-document-value-producin